# External Data & Integrations
- External data integrations inside the LMS application should be handled within REACT components
- Use bootstrap elements for loading states, status badges, and integration forms
- Wrap external interfaces (such as global PayPal and local RBI payment systems) within unified local service hooks
- Never print or pass sensitive transactional tokens, card numbers, or PII into open tracking logs
- Frequently accessed static matrices like help options must pull directly from a local static `FAQ.JSON` schema